headline: CSX secures tentative labor agreement with Boilermakers
summary: CSX (CSX) Corporation announced it has secured a new five-year tentative collective bargaining agreement with the International Brotherhood of Boilermakers, Iron Ship Builders, Blacksmiths, Forgers & Helpers, or IBB. The tentative agreement is subject to ratification by the union’s membership at CSX, accounting for 59 members.
